item.title: done today
item.description: 23:07 Monday 23 February 2015 JST Today I made a repo to help find particular md5 strings for Counting with md5sum. It’s my live md5 command line cheater. Also gave 10000 bit tip to a man who announced his wife was pregnant. And am working on a maze for Angelos, and printed a logo for a photo at Shibuya Crossing tomorrow. Okay good night!
